descriptionHtml:
If your are looking for a mobile speed boosting application then you have found it. 10 GB RAM Cleaner is the right application you are looking for, 10 GB RAM Cleaner is a mobile optimization app the speed ups your mobile speed by cleaning unused RAM of your mobile.
Powerful cleanup of memory. Just one tap start.
Special knowledge and settings are NOT needed!

Your phone will more smoothly run with RAM Cleanup!

Clean up (free up) the memory (RAM) to speed up (boost) your device with saving more battery and cooling down CPU. Just starting the app makes it easy to totally optimize your device.

You don't need any special knowledge for optimization of the smartphone system and performance.
You can remove the animation if you want.
Total memory reduction helps much faster operation with saving battery for gaming, browsing and OS itself.

Advanced functions:
-Auto closing.
-Auto clean function by recognition of exceeding threshold of memory usage ratio.
-Color settings for texts, background, foreground, and animation.
-Shortcut for customized cleanup.

Try this simple and light memory cleaner!

Function A:
- Stops all background services
- Stops all background Applications
- Stops all background processes
Function B:
- Clears trash files
- Remove useless installation packages
- Clears Temporary Files
- Delete Log files
- Clears Application caches files
- Process clean up
Function C:
- You can remove unwanted applications

10 GB RAM Cleaner is designed for new mobiles with latest OS up to android O Oreo devices. 10 GB RAM Cleaner supports mobile RAM up to 10 GB and it also works best for low RAM devices like 2GB, 4GB and 6GB

descriptionHtml:
The application is a mobile storage cleaner and performance monitor that helps users to clear their device's storage. The app scans the device for junk and unwanted files such as residual files, cache files, and temporary files and allows the user to delete them with just a few clicks. This frees up space on the device and helps it to save space for other application.

In addition to cleaning up the device, the app also provides real-time monitoring of the device's CPU temperature and RAM usage. The user can check the current temperature of their device's CPU and monitor the usage of their device's RAM in real-time.

Moreover, the app also allows the user to uninstall unwanted applications. It displays a list of all installed applications on the device, including their size and usage statistics, and allows the user to select and uninstall any of them with just a few taps.

The user-friendly interface of the app makes it easy for anyone to use it without any technical knowledge. With its efficient cleaning capabilities and performance monitoring features, this app is a must-have for anyone who wants to keep their device running smoothly and efficiently.

★How does this application clean your device?
Make your phone clean is the top priority of this cleaner. We have several features to help you to boost your device. No more bust & freeze.
✔ Clean cache – clean system cache & apps’ cache junk files to free up more space
✔ Clean apps' installation package – clean the installation apk of apps
✔ Clean uninstall remains-clean residual junk files from deleted apps

Your feedback always keeps us improving with more & more cool features.
descriptionShort: Free up your mobile storage with Junk file cleaner
title: Storage and Junk Cleaner
